constraints.ocl:
context BillOfMaterials
inv: self.items->notEmpty() implies self.items->sortedBy(x | x.name)->first().name <= self.items->sortedBy(x | x.name)->last().name

context BOMItem
inv: self.name.size() >= 10 implies self.name.substring(1, 10) = 'value'

context Machine
inv: self.sensors->notEmpty() implies self.sensors->last().type <> null

context Machine
inv: self.manufacturer <> null implies self.serialNumber <> null

context Supplier
inv: self.shipments->notEmpty() implies self.shipments->sortedBy(x | x.shipmentId)->first().shipmentId <= self.shipments->sortedBy(x | x.shipmentId)->last().shipmentId

context BillOfMaterials
inv: self.bomId.size() >= 5 implies self.bomId.substring(1, 5) = 'value'

context WorkOrder
inv: self.qualityChecks->notEmpty() implies self.qualityChecks->sortedBy(x | x.checkId)->first().checkId <= self.qualityChecks->sortedBy(x | x.checkId)->last().checkId

context Machine
inv: self.maintenanceTasks->forAll(x, y | x <> y implies x.scheduledAt <> y.scheduledAt)

context BillOfMaterials
inv: self.items->notEmpty() implies self.items->last().requiredQty <> null

context Workstation
inv: self.machines->forAll(x, y | x <> y implies x.manufacturer <> y.manufacturer)

context Machine
inv: self.maintenanceTasks->notEmpty() implies self.maintenanceTasks->last().isDone <> null

context Machine
inv: self.serialNumber.size() >= 6 implies self.serialNumber.substring(1, 6) = 'value'

context QualityCheck
inv: self.defects->includesAll(self.defects) or self.defects->excludesAll(self.defects)

context ProductionLine
inv: self.lineId.size() >= 5 implies self.lineId.substring(1, 5) = 'value'

context DefectReport
inv: self.defectId <> null and self.description <> null

context Technician
inv: self.tasks->includesAll(self.tasks) or self.tasks->excludesAll(self.tasks)

context QualityCheck
inv: self.defects->size() >= 2 and self.defects->size() <= 3

context Plant
inv: self.location.size() >= 5 implies self.location.substring(1, 5) = 'value'

context WorkOrder
inv: self.qualityChecks->forAll(x, y | x <> y implies x.checkedAt <> y.checkedAt)

context BOMItem
inv: self.name.size() >= 5 implies self.name.substring(1, 5) = 'value'

context Technician
inv: not(self.empId <> null implies self.name <> null)

context DefectReport
inv: not(self.description <> null and self.defectId <> null)

context Shift
inv: (self.operators->size() >= 1 and self.operators->size() <= 1) and (self.operators->size() < 1)

context DefectReport
inv: (self.severity >= 18 and self.severity <= 60) and (self.severity < 18)

context WorkOrder
inv: (self.qualityChecks->notEmpty() implies self.qualityChecks->first().passed <> null) and (self.qualityChecks->isEmpty())

context Product
inv: not((self.name <> null) = (self.sku <> null))
